I am new

Where and how to start

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="10/12" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs" el_class="mntbx-t700"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_position="left top"][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="6835" img_size="full" css_animation="bottom-to-top" enable_animation_pro="true" trigger_hook="0.45" duration="1100" el_class="mrg-n-t670" vertical_movement="-220"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="mrg-n-t670"][distance][subtitle subtitle_content="New here?"][vc_column_text enable_animation_pro="true" trigger_hook="0.35" duration="900" vertical_movement="90"]Hello and welcome to our church website, it’s always a real joy for us to meet and have new memebers in our church family. Here you will find useful information about our believe. Our mission is leading people in a growing relationship with Jesus Christ. Please join our church and start a new life. Whatever that next step is, it’s time to take a bold step of faith out of your comfort zone and discover what God has for you. We believe that you can’t go with God and stay where you are.[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_section wn_parallax="content-moving" wn_parallax_speed="190" css=".vc_custom_1484806937227{padding-top: 130px !important;padding-bottom: 130px !important;background-image: url(http://webnus.co/dummy/vision/discovery/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/tslider-bg.jpg?id=6853) !important;}"][vc_row layer_animation="true" css=".vc_custom_1485772783067{background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1480772617170{padding-top: 3% !important;padding-right: 15% !important;padding-bottom: 2% !important;padding-left: 15% !important;}"][distance type="5"][subtitle heading="2" subtitle_content="How is our church different than others?"][distance][vc_column_text]One of distinct thing about our church is what we’re an all- generations community. there’s a place for you here. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6" css=".vc_custom_1480754956343{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-right: 1% !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;padding-left: 19% !important;}"][vc_column_text]LOCATION

Sundays at 9:30 and 11:00 WWe are located at 12345 North No.28 – 63739 street lorem ipsum City, Country

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row layer_animation="true"][vc_column][distance][subtitle heading="2" subtitle_content="Starting point"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][vc_column_text]If you’re interested in getting connected at our church or involved in the life of the church, Starting Point is your first step. During our time together, you’ll meet our staff, learn how to get involved and understand key truths of the Christian faith. This class is designed to be a conversational environment where you discover more about our church and our mission as a church. Starting Point is held Sundays at 9:00 am in the Café and includes a free breakfast[/vc_column_text][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][vc_column_text]How do I get involved? There are many ways to get involved. Here are four of them: 1) Come to a worship service on the weekend. 2) Look into joining a Small Group, and get to know some great people. 3) Come to Wednesday Night Together, and enjoy a meal with the church family. 4) Find a Serve opportunity, Here, Near or Far.[/vc_column_text][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

[vc_row][vc_column][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row layer_animation="true"][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12" css=".vc_custom_1481716368454{border: 1px solid #e5e5e5 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="7559" img_size="full" el_class="img-trans-stl1"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12" css=".vc_custom_1481715950010{padding-left: 45px !important;}"][vc_row_inner white_text_color="yes" css=".vc_custom_1486298638859{margin-top: -70px !important;margin-left: -70px !important;padding-top: 11% !important;padding-right: 4% !important;padding-bottom: 14% !important;padding-left: 60px !important;}" el_class="colorb"][vc_column_inner][subtitle heading="1" subtitle_content="John Smith"][vc_column_text]
LEADER PASTOR
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][distance type="2"][vc_column_text]

Life Story

My wife, Amanda, and I married in 1980. Our daughter Sarah was born in USA in 2000 our son, David, was born in Fort Worth in 2005; and our daughter Lynda was born in Grapevine in 2006. What do you like to do in your free time? In my free time, I plan what I’m going to do the next time I have free time. Actually, I realize I’ll never get these days back with my kids, so my free time is mostly with Lynda and them. I enjoy running, cycling, watching movies and sports, cleaning my garage, and doing nothing. Job Description? We are seeking a full-time Children's Pastor to minister to children from birth through fifth grade. This individual will be responsible for recruitment, training and development of volunteer leaders in a church of 600. Primary objectives are to evangelize and disciple children and resource parents and families. Individual will implement and oversee the development of Orange Philosophy and oversee all aspects of programming on Mondays and Tuesdays. Successful candidates should demonstrate proven leadership abilities, be an effective communicator, energetic, highly creative, and able to plan and implement programs in a team-oriented environment. College degree and experience leading a vibrant children's ministry is preferred. Des Moines First Assembly is one church with two locations.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section css=".vc_custom_1483783237471{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][title_p_text top_title="Discover the church" top_title_part_1="An Overview About" top_title_part_2="Church Ministry"][distance type="5"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" layer_animation="true"][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="4/12"][ourteam type="4" img="7528" name="Lisa Norman" title="Children Minstry" social="enable" first_url="#" second_url="#"][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][vc_column_text]What is Children ministry about? Children’s Ministry exists to lead women in a growing relationship with Jesus Christ. We are friends: old friends making new friends, always allowing the circle to grow wider. We are sisters: accepting one another and challenging each other to grow in our faith. We are image-bearers: like Father, like daughter, we take Christ in us to our community, revealing His love and grace to a broken world. We hope you’ll join us as we grow in our relationship with Jesus together. If you have questions, please feel free to contact me. Let us think of ways to motivate one another to acts of love and good works. And let us not neglect our meeting together.   What do we care about? Experience heartfelt worship, good friends and a refreshing look into God’s Word in a comfortable, casual setting. Spring, Summer, and Fall semesters offered. Church is committed to coming alongside families in a way that helps strengthen and grow them. We look forward to connecting with you and growing with you as we experience God’s love together through moments. [/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section][vc_row layer_animation="true"][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text el_class="brdr-r1" css=".vc_custom_1483955705144{margin-right: 30px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;}"]

01. EXPLORE

Connecting Men

In ur church we believe that men ministry exists to connect you to God and also ministry is amazing community for people who want help.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text el_class="brdr-r1" css=".vc_custom_1483955877884{margin-right: 30px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;}"]

02. EMPOWER

Equipping Men

Our ministry exists to provide you with tools and resources to help you ignite your passions, deepen your faith in Jesus, and lead a purpose-driven life.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1483955860221{margin-right: 30px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;}"]

03. ENGAGE

Igniting Men

We believe our community gives you opportunities to express your shape for ministry and live your life on mission, empowering you to live boldly.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section css=".vc_custom_1483783237471{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][title_p_text align="center" top_title="Discover the church" top_title_part_1="An Overview About" top_title_part_2="Church Ministry"][distance type="5"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" layer_animation="true"][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="4/12"][ourteam type="4" img="7529" name="David Smith" title="Men Minstry" social="enable" first_url="#" second_url="#"][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][vc_column_text]What is Men ministry about? Men’s Ministry exists to lead women in a growing relationship with Jesus Christ. We are friends: old friends making new friends, always allowing the circle to grow wider. We are sisters: accepting one another and challenging each other to grow in our faith. We are image-bearers: like Father, like daughter, we take Christ in us to our community, revealing His love and grace to a broken world. We hope you’ll join us as we grow in our relationship with Jesus together. If you have questions, please feel free to contact me. Let us think of ways to motivate one another to acts of love and good works. And let us not neglect our meeting together.   What do we care about? Experience heartfelt worship, good friends and a refreshing look into God’s Word in a comfortable, casual setting. Spring, Summer, and Fall semesters offered. Church is committed to coming alongside families in a way that helps strengthen and grow them. We look forward to connecting with you and growing with you as we experience God’s love together through moments. item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!
